kelly-sentenced-to-30-years-in-prison-for-sex-trafficking-3258807">的监狱任期</a>同时服刑。 </p><figure id="attachment_3583878" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3583878" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3583878" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kanye-West@2000x1270.jpg" alt="坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）于2024年1月19日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶看到。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kanye-West@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kanye-West@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kanye-West@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kanye-West@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kanye-West@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kanye-West@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3583878" class="wp-caption-text">坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）于2024年1月19日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶看到。 （bellocqimages/bauer-griffin/GC图像的照片）</figcaption></figure><p>歌词是西方在写作“秃鹰”中遇到的许多争议之一。他最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-hits-out-at-antisemite-kanye-west-for-using-war-pigs-sample-without-permission-3585240">在未经允许的情况下使用了“钢铁侠”样本的奥兹·奥斯本（Ozzy Osbourne）的愤怒，</a>而沙龙告诉韦斯特（Sharon <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-osbourne-says-kanye-west-fucked-with-the-wrong-jew-this-time-3585447">）他“这次与错误的犹太人搞砸了”</a> 。此后，韦斯特（West <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-removes-sample-of-black-sabbaths-iron-man-after-ozzy-osbourne-criticism-3585627">）用自己的歌曲“ Hell of Life”的片段取代了样本</a>，该片段使用了合法清除的“钢铁侠”样本。</p><p>韦斯特最近还面临批评，因为他在裸体或露面的服装中分享了他的妻子的照片 - <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/system-of-a-downs-john-dolmayan-tells-kanye-west-show-some-class-man-3567248">唐·唐·迪尔玛扬（John Dolmayan）的系统告诉他“展示一些班级</a>”，并补充说：奖杯，她是您的骄傲和尊严的地方。这不是方式”。</p><p>在其他新闻中，韦斯特暗示了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-shares-potential-cities-for-uk-us-and-world-vultures-tour-with-ty-dolla-ign-3583789">与ty dolla $ ign的潜在“秃鹰”世界巡回演唱</a>会。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_91 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_91" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/music/uk-government-calling-for-evidence-from-women-asked-to-sign-ndas-to-silence-sexual-assault-accusations-in-music-industry-3544547"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><h3><strong>有关帮助，建议或更多有关在英国性骚扰，攻击和强奸的信息，请访问<a href="https://rapecrisis.org.uk/find-a-centre/">强奸危机慈善网站</a>。在美国，参观<a href="https://www.rainn.org/index.php">雷恩</a>。</strong></h3></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-compares-himself-to-r-kelly-and-bill-cosby-on-new-album-3585624">坎耶·韦斯特（Kanye West）的《新专辑》（R. Kelly）和比尔·科斯比（Bill Cosby）在新专辑中</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
